title: Fix for code generation bug in VS2019 with inlining code is still needed with 16.5
message:
Fix for code generation bug in VS2019 with inlining code is still needed with 16.5

cf. commit 52834b21591bb0d6d323e3948bf59e4b969af385 and <https://developercommunity.visualstudio.com/content/problem/865092/bad-codegen-after-update-to-vc-2019-164-with-ob2-f.html>.
